title: Turkey & Bacon Egg Bites Board The perfect on-the-go breakfast. | 4 Servings
description: Not a morning person? We hear you! Luckily, we've cracked the code to make your morning so much easier (and more delicious). Enter four pillowy sous-vide egg bites: two loaded with turkey sausage and cheddar cheese and two with bacon and cheddar. They're ridiculously simple to whip up—all you have to do is heat and eat! Dip them into your favorite sauce, pair them with toast, or simply pop 'em on the go. There's no wrong way to do it.

